{"tid":1309504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：中國未兌現購農產品承諾","createTime":"2019-07-12T08:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T08:49:49.000Z","uid":30561,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9afefb3df3c5981ec1afbf582439baf8d80fdb4","tid":1309504,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/7/1562897820_oe-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F7%2F1562897820_oe-1280w.jpg&h=a83ef840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在美中雙方將重啟貿易之際，美國總統特朗普在社交專頁指中國未有遵守承諾，向美國農夫採購農產品，令美方失望，希望中方很快會開始採購。特朗普在同一則帖文中，稱讚墨西哥在美墨邊境問題上做得很好。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普與中國國家人主席習近平月初在大阪G20峰會會面後，特朗普舉行記者會時表示，自己與習近平進行了「非常好的會談」。他承諾，將不會對餘下3,250億元的中國進口美國貨品加徵關稅，並稱中國很快會向美國購入很多食物及農產品。"},{"pid":"276900ef76b4a0543ca155a3221a8b4d67b91c7a","tid":1309504,"uid":19557,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:38:22.000Z","msg":"希望支拿又反口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfef0299c04e00cb838a8dad54ca761997472f08","tid":1309504,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c6e0ad411b4451a1f35f0df4b86950f40910a8","tid":1309504,"uid":46464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"又撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e842390f170854fc20711aee3570dbd603c3c0","tid":1309504,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:39:19.000Z","msg":"又想打"},{"pid":"65a526c8e08ab54a25d169c1a09601f5d39daf4f","tid":1309504,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddfb3f3c781e360a428775b4e8af5bb341425f2","tid